  "prompt": "Who created Quora?",
  "response": "Quora was created in 2009 by Adam D'Angelo and Charlie Cheever, both former employees of Facebook. Adam D'Angelo, who previously served as Facebook's Chief Technology Officer (CTO), took on the role of CEO at Quora. The platform was launched to provide a space where people can ask questions and receive answers from others in a community-driven environment. Since its inception, Quora has grown into a widely used question-and-answer website covering a vast array of topics.",
